# Forms folder — Durham

No Durham-specific TPI/SI form was located on durhamnc.gov or dconc.gov as of 2026-04-27. Default fallback is the NC State Construction Office Statement of Special Inspections template:
https://www.doa.nc.gov/documents/files/sco-statement-special-inspections-rev-february-2020-docx/open

Confirm directly with Chief Building Inspector Wyatt Blalock (wyatt.blalock@durhamnc.gov) before submission.
